<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.3">
<l>tiṇṇak kalattil tiraiyuṟi mēlvaitta</l>
<l>veṇṇey viḻuṅki virai yuṟaṅkiṭu</l>
<l>maṇṇa lamarar perumāṉai yāyartaṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉai vantukuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">kārmukilvaṇ ṇaṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come to Kaṇṇaṉ of the cowherders,</l>
<l rend="indent">the great lord of the celestials who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having devoured the butter</l>
<l rend="indent">placed in swaying nets in robust pots,</l>
<l rend="indent">promplty went to sleep</l>
<l>Caw! Caw!Comb [his] curly hair.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw!Comb the curly hair of him with the black cloud complexion.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
